Are you guys still playing EQ? hehe<br>As you
know, I had stopped playing for a while... however, I
came back. I now have a lvl 47 druid on the Lanys
T'vyl server (no I didn't buy an account ;P ). I like
the server much better than Mith Marr because there
is much less guild rivalry and competition over phat
lewt. Let me know how you guys are doing! =)<br><br> -
Gilerrin Galewind, lvl 42 ranger (retired)<br> - Kanadin
Starchaser, lvl 47 Druid of Tunare
